    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; color:#2F3A4A;">
      AppliedAM is built on real contributions from the AM community. Whether you are a researcher with new findings, a manufacturer with a production story, or a practitioner with a completed project — we want to hear from you.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; color:#2F3A4A;">
      Submissions are reviewed for technical merit and published with full attribution. Getting featured on AppliedAM is free, permanent, and citable.
    </p>
